{
  "stem": "22840.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not conservative in the American sense.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was orthodox in the American sense-- even very orthodox in the American sense, but not orthodox in the-- in the-- in the European sense.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that because they gave him a lot of trouble.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I recalled that even before the war, before-- before the German invasion, he was referring to them as the 45's. 45 was the caliber of a big gun.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- they gave him a lot of trouble because they were not Zionist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a clash between the Zionist rabbis and Zionist movement and the strict orthodoxy, the Hasidic orthodoxy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was it was a-- it was an ideological clash, and one which continues still today.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very active in-- in-- in the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very active in the Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He tried to resurrect the Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very active in the political life of the country, but he died very quickly after that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the exception of the low countries that we called-- they called it low.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, not low-- not low culturally, low physically, Denmark, Holland, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With the exception of those countries and then some of the Scandinavians, obviously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Scandinavians.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Europe has nothing to be proud of for their conduct in the Second World War, relative to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with the current revelations about the information which is available today lies I think the dark part of the history of mankind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I recall going to the circus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can actually recall going to movies, I recall going to school, sliding down the side of the mountain in the winter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, yes, it was-- it was very normal.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
